# Bridge to AGENTS.md

The source of truth for this repository's instructions is [`AGENTS.md`](./AGENTS.md).

Read `AGENTS.md` before any action. It is an always-on index and points to the context layer in `ai-context/` — including `ai-context/ARCHITECTURE.md`, `ai-context/CONVENTIONS.md` and the detailed rules in `ai-context/rules/`, which must be read on the first interaction of the session.

This file only exists to ensure that the agent reading this filename by convention (CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md, GEMINI.md, .cursorrules, .windsurfrules, copilot-instructions.md) is redirected to the source of truth. Do not duplicate rules here.
